  <!-- EN:
    <li>questDescription->A Wolfein resistance officer has decided to employ their renowned expertise in toxic gas warfare to launch an attack on the colony. A toxic gas generator has been constructed near the colony, continuously releasing lethal poisonous dust into the surrounding area.\n\nWhile the device remains operational, the colony will be shrouded in toxic haze. The generator must be destroyed as soon as possible, before the gas causes irreversible damage.\n\nIntelligence reports indicate that resistance forces have been deployed around the generator to guard the installation.</li>
